creator: FaWorkshop
descriptionHtml:
FaLala stickers collection for WhatsApp. Designed by J.Pictures.

You can use these stickers in the latest version of WhatsApp.

Send them to your friends and family!

More stories of FaLala:
https://www.instagram.com/j.pictures.falala/
https://www.facebook.com/Jada40416/

------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------------
How to use:
- Download and open this app
- Tap on 'ADD TO WHATSAPP'
- Confirm your action
- Open WhatsApp and go to a chat
- Tap on the Emoji icon
- You will see a new sticker icon at the bottom and can now use this sticker pack
